           --> SC Simplified Chinese 寿命 shòu mìng TC Traditional Chinese 壽命  (人)
 -- The average human lifespan is increasing in most countries.
 -- 在多数国家，人的平均寿命都在不断增长。
 
lifespan, life span n (goods: duration)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 寿命, 使用期限  (货物)
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 保质期 bǎo zhì qī TC Traditional Chinese 貨質期 
 -- These snacks have a lifespan of only a couple of weeks.
 -- 这些点心的保质期不过几周而已。
 
lifespan, life span n (period of existence)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 周期, 生命周期  
 -- A total of €2.5 million will be invested over the lifespan of the project.
 -- 在该项目的整个生命周期内，将总共投资250万英镑。
 
spick and span, spick-and-span adj informal (clean, neat)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 干净的，整洁的 gān jìng de ，zhěng jié de TC Traditional Chinese 乾淨的，整潔的  
 -- 备注 : Hyphens are used when the adjective precedes the noun
 
