           --> SC Simplified Chinese 时长 shí cháng  
 "" 
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 时间段 shí cháng，shí jiān duàn 
 
timespan, time span n (period of time, duration)
           --> SC Simplified Chinese 时间跨度 shí jiān kuà dù TC Traditional Chinese 時間跨度  
